3
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:11,600
But what happens when insulin production falters?

4
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:13,200
That's linked to diabetes.

5
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:18,400
Recent studies suggest the pancreas can adapt, but this is still being explored.

